Package: kernel-autotune
Version: 2.2.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Bobby Comet
Depends: bash, procps, coreutils, util-linux
Description: Intelligent kernel tuning with predictable behavior and safety.
 Includes automated SSD detection, NUMA handling, and ZRAM/ZSWAP
 coordination. Version 2.2.0 introduces exclusive execution locking,
 a dry-run mode for safe testing, and enhanced hardware probing for
 handhelds and laptops.
